description:
Looking for courtroom action? We are a practice of 25 civil trial attorneys seeking to hire several attorneys from entry-level to 10+ years of experience to work with our 12 Certified Civil Trial Attorneys in preparing and trying personal injury trials.



A comprehensive benefits package is available.


**Responsibilities:*** A strong desire to help clients;
* Willingness to be part of a winning team;
* Unique understanding of building and proving damage models;
* Legal intelligence in formulating case strategies;
* Good writing, organization, computer skills, and work ethic;
* Strong desire to win results on behalf of injured clients;
* Strong desire to work with the latest cutting-edge technologies;
* Second language skills are a plus;
* Plaintiff or Defense experience;
* Proven track record;
* Experience with injury cases;
* Federal Court experience a plus;
* Winning record.

**Qualifications:****Experienced Attorney with 3-5 years Personal Injury Experience**

* Admission to NJ Bar (NY not necessary but a plus);
* Plaintiff or defense experience;
* Ability to handle and manage a personal injury case list at all stages;
* Solid legal knowledge of NJ MVA and premises jurisprudence;
* Understanding of legal medicine;
* Deposition, Arbitration, dispositive motion experience;
* Experience prepping cases for trial.

 **Experienced Trial Attorney with 10-plus years of Personal Injury Experience**

* New Jersey Admission (NY a plus);
* Civil Trial Certification or eligibility;
* Medical Malpractice Experience and/ Product Liability;
* Proven Track Record;
* Experienced with managing catastrophic and serious injury cases;
* Federal Court Experience a plus;
* Good writing skills;
* Winning record;
* Solid work ethic.

**About Company**  

Leading personal injury law firm based in North New Jersey, dedicated to providing exceptional legal representation and client-focused service. With over 100 employees, our firm is committed to achieving outstanding results for clients while maintaining a collaborative and dynamic work environment.
